HEADWORD: Thrid
<hw>Thrid</hw> <pr>(thr⟦icr⟧d)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Third.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
